Additional Terms for Correctional Facility Use:

This software is designed for use in correctional facilities and handles sensitive 
institutional data. Users of this software must:

1. Comply with all applicable local, state, and federal regulations regarding 
   correctional facility operations and data privacy.

2. Implement appropriate security measures to protect sensitive inmate and 
   institutional data.

3. Ensure proper authorization and administrative approval before deployment 
   in any correctional facility environment.

4. Maintain data confidentiality and follow institutional policies regarding 
   information security and access controls.

5. Regularly update and maintain the system to address security vulnerabilities 
   and ensure continued compliance with relevant regulations.

The authors and contributors of this software are not responsible for any 
misuse, security breaches, or regulatory non-compliance resulting from 
improper implementation or use of this system.

For questions regarding compliance or security requirements, please consult 
with appropriate legal and technical authorities within your jurisdiction.

